optimal_awakening_growths.passive_skill_description:
Ki +4 and ATK & DEF +170%; randomly changes 
Ki Spheres of a certain Type to Rainbow Ki Spheres 
when there is another "Super Heroes" Category ally 
on the team; plus an additional Ki +2 per 
Rainbow Ki Sphere obtained; plus an additional 
ATK & DEF +7% per Ki Sphere obtained; chance of 
performing a critical hit +7%, reduces damage received by 7% 
and launches an additional attack that has a high chance 
of becoming a Super Attack (up to 3 additional attacks 
within a turn) per Rainbow Ki Sphere obtained; 
plus an additional ATK & DEF +70% if Ki is 18 or more; 
reduces damage received by 70% when HP is 50% or less 
(once only) and performs a critical hit if Ki is 24
